School of Geosciences
Relative sea-level and therefore accommodation space, together with sediment supply vary over a number of different time-scales.
Small-scale sequence stratigraphical depositional units (parasequences) stack together due to changes in accommodation space and/or sediment supply over longer time periods to form sequences.
Development of parasequences
